{"id":232760369,"title":"寫在聖誕的《燃燒女子的畫像》","content":"https://i.imgur.com/HZRJzjY.jpg\nhttps://i.imgur.com/0t5OwAV.jpg\n  在聖誕夜邂逅了瑪麗安娜躍動閃爍的眼睛，如果我有幸身為模特，肯定會被瑪麗安娜的眼睛給迷到。\n  喜歡《燃燒女子的畫像》的簡單，它很好地還原了一段也許只有圈內人才懂的，刻骨銘心的記憶。以藝術的方式談情說愛，以靜態如畫般的美感取代本該激烈如火的肉體慾望。我想這就是讓藝術與禁忌之戀的結合深具魅力的原因。\n  然而我對它的喜愛，其實並沒有到“多刷幾次”的程度，相反，我更珍惜第一次看它的經歷，咀嚼，存取它的每一句話，每一處景，而它，也是我們每一個人都能擁有，甚至寫作的回憶。\n  愛了卻不能被實現，明知這段戀愛不會有結果卻偏要愛，都很痛。於是我也像瑪麗安娜，轉過身，步履沈重又匆匆，頭也不回地離開，這個本不屬於自己的世界。","excerpt":"在聖誕夜邂逅了瑪麗安娜躍動閃爍的眼睛，如果我有幸身為模特，肯定會被瑪麗安娜的眼睛給迷到。喜歡《燃燒女子的畫像》的簡單，它很好地還原了一段也許只有圈內人才懂的，刻骨銘心的記憶。以藝術的方式談情說愛，以靜","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"26e4252c-63d8-401b-82a9-110fe1e306db","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-25T15:33:50.158Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-25T15:33:50.158Z","commentCount":4,"likeCount":49,"tags":[],"topics":["Les","愛情","彩虹"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"Les","forumAlias":"lesbian","school":"中國文化大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":49}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/HZRJzjY.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/0t5OwAV.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"f01fdd48-341f-4c84-a013-b31ab63ba152","url":"https://i.imgur.com/HZRJzjYl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/HZRJzjYl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/HZRJzjYl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-25T15:33:50.158Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-25T15:33:50.158Z"},{"id":"f01fdd48-341f-4c84-a013-b31ab63ba152","url":"https://i.imgur.com/HZRJzjY.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/HZRJzjY","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/HZRJzjYl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-25T15:33:50.158Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-25T15:33:50.158Z"},{"id":"5676f4f9-e32